ript.\\n- Each object in the `JSON` will represent metrics of one run for a single library version.\\n- Example:\\n  - `script_run_metrics/new_library_support.json` – metrics for a script that manages or tests adding new library support.\\n\\n### `benchmark_run_metrics/`\\n\\nStores metrics from predefined benchmark configurations.\\n\\n- Each benchmark has a JSON file named after it.\\n- Example:\\n  - `benchmark_run_metrics/metadata_entries_hunter.json` – metrics for a benchmark suite that tracks performance or behavior when adding new library support, using a strategy that favors generating tests which tend to cover as many metadata entries as possible.\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_24\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"jackson-annotations|2.3.0|1999\\\" /home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/1999-4c0ff9fe/script_run_metrics'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_24\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'rg -n \\\"jackson-annotations|2.3.0|1999\\\" /home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/1999-4c0ff9fe/script_run_metrics'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"/home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/1999-4c0ff9fe/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:444:    \\\"library\\\": \\\"com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-annotations:2.1.2\\\",\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/1999-4c0ff9fe/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json:492:      \\\"test_file\\\": \\\"tests/src/com.fasterxml.jackson.core/jackson-annotations/2.1.2/src/test/java/com_fasterxml_jackson_core/jackson_annotations/Jackson_annotationsTest.java\\\",\\n/home/vjovanov/c/forge1/metadata-forge/local_repositories/forge_run_metr